{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MS05_130.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x11,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Sophie, what do you think about your current armor?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "It's very easy to move around in and use."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Hehe, really? But there's actually something I'm concerned about."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Lately, whenever we go gathering, I feel like our armor isn't strong enough."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "It would be nice if I could make better stuff, but... Unlike clothes, I don't have many good ideas about armor."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Also, we would probably need to use better materials to make it more effective."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "It's true that we're fighting strong monsters more often now. We might need something better..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "I know! In that case, could you enhance our armor?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Enhance it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. Alchemy actually allows you to enhance items to be more effective."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I was wondering if it would be possible to do the same thing with armor."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I see... I might be able to do that with the materials we have now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "We should try it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "I'm really attached to the armor I have now, so I'd be happier if we could get stronger together."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "You can now Enhance armor at Leon's shop."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "You can enhance your armor's stats by using (Cloth) category items on it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "The number of times armor can be enhanced varies, and enhanced stats depend on quality and traits."
        }
    ]
}